Adding and subtracting n bits using 1 full adder. 

The size of register can be changed according to number of bits and the value in for loop must also be changed. 

This result will be displayed in binary with LSB first and followed by more significant bits.

fullAdder.v is the main function file

t_adder.v is test bench for full adder

t_subtractor.v is test bench for full subtractor

vvp files are the output files

vcd files are the gtkwave files
